 libyaml-0-2, libssl3, libpam0g
Description: Modern PostgreSQL connection pooler with REST API
 pgbalancer is a modern, production-ready PostgreSQL connection pooler and
 load balancer built as a fork of pgpool-II. It provides a comprehensive
 REST API, professional CLI tool, and YAML configuration support.
 .
 Features:
  * Production HTTP/JSON REST API (17 endpoints)
  * Unified CLI tool (bctl) replacing pcp_* commands
  * YAML configuration with validation
  * Optional pgraft consensus integration
  * AI-based load balancing algorithms
  * JWT authentication for API security
  * Connection pooling and load balancing
  * Automatic failover and recovery
  * Health monitoring and performance statistics
  * Compatible with PostgreSQL 13, 14, 15, 16, 17, 18

